Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:19.65,TypePlaceholder,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman Bold\fs18\fsp1\fad(0,0)\bord1\shad1\c&HC1C4C0&\3c&H201F19&\4c&H131313&\pos(146,243)}Revision & Typesetting:\NJacqueline Philippi
